---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import CriteriaLab from "../components/CriteriaLab.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Kur'an Yapısal Kodlamaları ile Mod 7 ve Mod 19 Bulguları"
  description="Kur'an yapısal kodlamalarını, Mod 19 bulgularını, Ha-Mim bağlantılarını, fihrist bulgularını ve ilgili kriter kümelerini ayrı bir araştırma sayfasında inceleyin."
>
  <section class="criteria-page">
    <div class="criteria-page__topbar">
      <a class="criteria-page__back" href="/">
        <span data-copy-lang="tr">Ana sayfaya dön</span>
        <span data-copy-lang="en">Back to homepage</span>
      </a>
    </div>

    <section class="criteria-page__method" aria-label="Metodoloji notu">
      <p class="criteria-page__method-kicker">
        <span data-copy-lang="tr">Metin temeli</span>
        <span data-copy-lang="en">Text basis</span>
      </p>

      <p class="criteria-page__method-text">
        <span data-copy-lang="tr">
          Bu sayfadaki harf ve ayet temelli hesaplamalarda esas alınan metin tabanı, Corpus Coranicum TEI aktarımı içindeki
          1924 Kahire Mushafı'dır (Kral Fuad / Bulak baskısı).
        </span>
        <span data-copy-lang="en">
          The primary textual basis used for the letter- and verse-level calculations on this page is the 1924 Cairo muṣḥaf
          (King Fuad / Bulaq edition) as represented in the Corpus Coranicum TEI transcription.
        </span>
      </p>

      <p class="criteria-page__method-text criteria-page__method-text--subtle">
        <span data-copy-lang="tr">
          Fihrist dizilimleri ve bazı arşiv testleri repo içindeki doğrulama çıktılarıyla sunulur; metodolojik referans yine aynı mushaf tabanıdır.
        </span>
        <span data-copy-lang="en">
          Fihrist sequences and some archive tests are surfaced through repository snapshots and verification outputs; the methodological reference remains the same muṣḥaf base.
        </span>
      </p>
    </section>

    <CriteriaLab />
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .criteria-page {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    width: min(1540px, calc(100vw - 1.5rem));
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 5.5rem 0 3rem;
  }

  .criteria-page__topbar {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: flex-start;
    gap: 0.85rem;
  }

  .criteria-page__back {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding-bottom: 0.2rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--theme-border);
    color: var(--theme-ink-soft);
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .criteria-page__back:hover {
    color: var(--theme-ink-strong);
    border-color: var(--theme-border-strong);
  }

  .criteria-page__method {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.35rem;
    padding: 0.15rem 0 0.95rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--theme-border);
  }

  .criteria-page__method-kicker {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--theme-muted);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .criteria-page__method-text {
    max-width: 76rem;
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--theme-ink-soft);
    font-size: 0.94rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .criteria-page__method-text--subtle {
    color: var(--theme-muted);
    font-size: 0.86rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 780px) {
    .criteria-page {
      width: min(100vw - 1rem, 100%);
      padding-top: 5rem;
    }

    .criteria-page__topbar {
      align-items: start;
    }

    .criteria-page__method {
      padding-bottom: 0.8rem;
    }

    .criteria-page__method-text {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      line-height: 1.65;
    }
  }
</style>
